# ------------------------------------------------------
# 1. IGNORE EVERYTHING IN THE PROJECT ROOT
# ------------------------------------------------------
# This blocks venv, scrapers, node_modules, python scripts, etc.
**/**

# ------------------------------------------------------
# 2. EXCEPTION: ALLOW THE APPS SCRIPT FOLDER
# ------------------------------------------------------
